          "settings": {
            "title": "Women’s Wetsuits & Spring Suits | Sustainable Surf Swimwear",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": true,
            "text": "<p>Our women’s wetsuit and spring suit collection is made for ocean-loving women who demand both performance and style. Crafted from eco-friendly limestone neoprene, these suits provide the perfect balance of warmth, flexibility, and a sculpting fit - whether you’re surfing, swimming, or enjoying a morning SUP session.</p><p>Designed to feel like a second skin, our spring suits for women offer UPF 50+ sun protection, a sleek silhouette, and a secure fit that stays put through every duck dive. The 2.5mm thickness keeps you warm in cooler conditions while allowing complete freedom of movement.</p>",
