            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>This collection was inspired by the women in our Ocean Soul community - surfers, divers, water lovers, and sun-conscious adventurers who wanted more from their wetsuits. You asked for a wetsuit that sculpts and performs, feels good on your skin, looks beautiful, and aligns with your values. We listened.</p><p>Whether you're just starting your surf journey or spend every weekend in the sea, these suits give you support, warmth, and freedom - without compromise.</p><p><strong>All suits feature:</strong></p><p>Premium YKK zips<br/></p><p>High necklines for warmth and protection<br/></p><p>Secure leg openings that stay put through movement<br/></p><p>Streamlined, functional silhouettes with surf performance in mind</p><p>Whether you're just starting your surf journey or spend every weekend in the sea, these suits give you support, warmth, and freedom - without compromise.</p>",
