            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Available in both long sleeve wetsuit styles and chic short-cut spring suits, our designs are panelled to flatter your shape, double-lined for comfort, and finished with premium YKK zips for durability. Choose from timeless black, bold cherry red, or shimmering metallic tones like gold and titanium to make a statement in and out of the water.</p><p>Ethically made in Bali in small batches, each Ocean Soul wetsuit combines function, form, and sustainability - so you can feel confident in your gear and your impact.</p><p>From the lineup to the beach, these are women’s wetsuits that perform beautifully and last season after season.</p>",
