            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<h2>Why Choose an Ocean Soul Women’s Wetsuit or Spring Suit?</h2><p>SUSTAINABLE LIMESTONE NEOPRENE</p><p>Our wetsuits are crafted from Eco-prene, a limestone-based neoprene alternative that’s more sustainable than petroleum-based rubber. Paired with GT3 recycled lining made from post-consumer plastic bottles, our suits are warmer, lighter, and better for the planet  - without compromising performance.</p><p></p>",
