            "title": "How warm are the limestone wetsuits?",
            "content": "<p>Our womens wetsuits are both 2.5mm and insulated with PET lining. They are the perfect spring suit for in between seasons.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_gjFzLG": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How durable are the spring suits for water sports?",
            "content": "<p>Our spring suits are made from durable, limestone-based Eco-prene neoprene, designed to last through intense water sports like surfing, paddleboarding, and freediving. Its high-quality construction with PK Zips and are constructed with Triple Glue blind stitched. Which means this <strong>spring suit</strong> will stay strong and flexible, session after session.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_MMjzfc": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How should I care for my women’s wetsuit to make it last longer?",
            "content": "<p>To extend the life of your <strong>women’s wetsuit</strong>, it’s essential to rinse it with fresh water after each use to remove salt, sand, and chlorine. Hang it in a shaded area to dry, avoiding direct sunlight to prevent damage to the Eco-prene neoprene. </p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_kXUL7y": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "I'm not sure what size I am in wetsuit",
            "content": "<p>We have our size chart for the Neoprene <a href=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/pages/size-guide-wetsuits\" title=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/pages/size-guide-wetsuits\">here. </a></p><p>You can also reach out to us directly for further assistance via <a href=\"/pages/contact-us\" title=\"Contact Us\">email.</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_hWhfeR": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I return it if it's not the right size or if I don't like it?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely!  Process all returns via our website portal <a href=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/a/returns\" title=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/a/returns\">here.</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_GfcmfX": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are these spring suits only for surfing and diving?",
            "content": "<p>Our spring suits are designed for all water lovers!  Some of our customers buy them just for snorkelling or swimming when the water is cold.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_CWNBa6": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "What should I do if my wetsuit develops creases",
            "content": "<p>Creasing is a normal occurrence with <strong>spring suits</strong> and other wetsuits, especially after storing them folded. To reduce creases, store your wetsuit by hanging it on a thick, wide hanger. Over time, any minor creases will smooth out, but proper storage helps maintain the suit’s form.</p>"
          }
        },
